  "title": "Assistant Sales Manager #77419",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Electronics Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Assistant Sales Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bendemeer</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon - Fri, 8.00am - 5.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $5,000 + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage assigned customer accounts, including customer relationships, forecasting to the factory, inventory management, and meeting monthly sales targets.</li><li>Coordinate with the factory and Japan headquarters on shipment schedules, sample requests, and R&D activities.</li><li>Support sales activities with existing and new customers to create new business opportunities.</li><li>Assist the Finance Department with accounts receivable collection from customers.</li><li>Be willing to travel in the region to support customers or follow up on sales leads.</li><li>Help the Sales Manager with preparing sales reports.</li><li>Be open to traveling overseas, especially to India and Indonesia, to explore new business opportunities.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or degree in Sales, Marketing, or Engineering.</li><li>Able to work independently and has strong interpersonal skills.</li><li>Preferably has B2B sales experience in manufacturing, especially with experience in supporting customer design projects.</li><li>Familiar with trading terms and conditions, and comfortable using Microsoft Office and Google productivity tools.</li><li>Technical knowledge of mechanical products is an added advantage.</li><li>Experience with Salesforce or SAP is an advantage.</li><li>Experience in the electronics manufacturing industry is a plus.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77419 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
